00:21:51,957 --> 00:21:52,337
Esatto.

466
00:21:52,577 --> 00:21:53,458
Eh, certo.

467
00:21:53,857 --> 00:21:54,999
Il malosti pensiero.

468
00:21:55,078 --> 00:21:55,398
Giusto.

469
00:21:56,919 --> 00:21:58,940
Gli esseri umani, meglio evitarli.

470
00:21:59,299 --> 00:22:00,079
Sempre.

